{"article_id":"6Dm88k0Cb1a6yHn1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The sex-crimes prosecutor Republicans","depth":11},{"id":1,"text":"hired to question Brett Kavanaugh and accuser Christine Blasey Ford at Thursday 's hearing","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"told senators","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"the case would not hold up in a courtroom ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"sources told Fox News-guidance","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that could prove critical","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"as wavering lawmakers prepare to vote .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"The prosecutor , Rachel Mitchell , spoke at an overnight meeting","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"where all 51 Republican senators were present ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"two people","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"briefed on the session","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"said .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"\" Mitchell spelled it out","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"and was clear with senators","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"that she could not take this anywhere near a courtroom , \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"one source told Fox News .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"She told them","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"she would not charge the Supreme Court nominee","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and reportedly said","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"she would n't even seek a search warrant .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"Mitchell ' s opinion could sway fence-sitting senators ahead of a critical Senate Judiciary Committee vote","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"set for Friday afternoon .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"It is not necessary for Kavanaugh to secure majority approval of the committee","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"in order to advance to the full Senate ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"but a favorable recommendation could bode well for his imperiled nomination","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"-- and vice-versa .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"In a critical development , Republican Sen. Jeff Flake announced Friday morning","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"he will support Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"saying ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` I left the hearing yesterday with as much doubt as certainty . ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"With that , 48 Republican senators have now pledged to vote for Kavanaugh at the scheduled full Senate vote on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"The outstanding Republicans are Sens . Susan Collins of Maine , Lisa Murkowski of Alaska , and Mike Enzi of Wyoming .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Enzi is expected to vote in support of Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"but has said","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"he won ' t announce his position","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"until he votes .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"But Collins , Murkowski , Flake and Democratic Sen. Joe Manchin could vote in a bloc .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"The source told Fox News","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that Collins , Murkowski and Flake huddled with Manchin on the sidelines Thursday evening","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to discuss the nomination ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"right before the GOP lawmakers were briefed by Mitchell .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"They spoke for approximately 30 minutes .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"\" It ' s a tough one .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"She offered good testimony ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and so did he , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Flake ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"who sits on the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"said Thursday night ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"before announcing his support .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" If you ' re making an allegation ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"you want there to be some corroboration .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Where is the burden ?","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"It ' s like impeachment .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"You don ' t know . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"including President Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"have stressed","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that none of the sexual misconduct allegations against Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"made in the last several days","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"have first-hand corroboration .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"But Ford insisted during Thursday 's testimony","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that Kavanaugh and a friend trapped her in a room during a high school gathering in 1982 ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and the now-court nominee tried to force himself on her","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"before she escaped .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"she 's `` 100 percent '' sure","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"it was him ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"though Kavanaugh adamantly denied it .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Asked whether more time or investigating would help ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"as Democrats suggested repeatedly on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Flake rejected the idea .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"\" Where does this start ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"where does it end ? \"","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"he asked .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" More time , more ludicrous allegations .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"What does that do to the accused ? \"","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Manchin , from deep-red West Virginia , is seen as a possible `` yea '' vote for Kavanaugh .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"\" There have been no decisions , \"","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"Manchin reportedly said outside the hearing room .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"\" There are some concerns","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"that people have ,","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"and we ' re going to try to close that loop . \"","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"Democratic Sens . Heidi Heitkamp of North Dakota and Joe Donnelly of Indiana also have not revealed","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"which way they might vote .","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"Early Friday , Sen. Bill Nelson , D-Fla. , said","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"that he would vote \" no . \"","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"Republicans hold a narrow 51-49 majority in the Senate ,","depth":4},{"id":87,"text":"and can only afford one defection in their bid","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"to confirm Kavanaugh ,","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"assuming","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"they secure no Democratic votes .","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"Other Republican senators","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"whose votes were expected to be up in the air ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"like Sens . Bob Corker , came out in support of Kavanaugh late Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"\" While both individuals provided a compelling testimony ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"nothing","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that has been presented","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"corroborates the allegation , \"","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Corker said in a statement ,","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"referring to Kavanaugh and Ford .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"Kavanaugh vehemently denied the allegations","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"leveled against him by Ford ,","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"calling the process a \" national disgrace \" and a \" circus . \"","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"\" The Constitution gives the Senate an important role in the confirmation process , \"","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Kavanaugh said in his opening statement .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"\" But you have replaced advise and consent with search and destroy . \"","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , announced late Thursday a full Senate vote for Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"we ' re going to go ahead , \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch , R-Utah , said .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"\" I worry about every one of these votes . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":221,"left":196,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":186,"right":195,"relat